verses.rendering:
They strengthen each other in an evil plan;
they talk about hiding their traps.
They say, "Who can see us?"

They devise injustice after injustice;
they complete their carefully searched-out scheme.
The inner mind and heart of a person run deep.

Then all people stand in awe
and declare what God has done;
they understand his work.

The righteous one rejoices in the LORD
and takes refuge in him;
all the upright in heart celebrate.
